    "content": "\n<p>When we started working with a business selling over WhatsApp, the technology wasn't the problem. The manual effort between the systems was. This is how we turned that friction into an automated workflow — and what it changed.</p>\n<h2>The Problem</h2>\n<ul><li>High-intent chats lost in a flooded WhatsApp inbox</li><li>No structured capture or qualification</li><li>Follow-ups forgotten between conversations</li><li>No visibility into what was working</li></ul>\n<h2>What We Automated</h2>\n<p>Rather than rip out the tools the team already relied on, we connected them with AI agents that handle the repetitive work end to end:</p>\n<h3>Enquiry capture</h3><p>Every WhatsApp lead is logged automatically.</p><h3>Qualification</h3><p>Conversations are qualified without manual triage.</p><h3>Automated follow-up</h3><p>Timed nudges keep deals moving inside the chat.</p><h3>Reporting</h3><p>Owners finally see what WhatsApp is producing.</p>\n<h2>The Results</h2>\n<ul><li>High-intent chats captured, not buried</li><li>Structured qualification inside WhatsApp</li><li>Follow-ups that actually happen</li><li>Clear visibility into the channel's revenue</li></ul>\n<h2>Why It Matters</h2>\n<p>Meet customers where they already are — and make that channel work as hard as your CRM.</p>\n<h2>Could This Work in Your Business?</h2>\n<p>If you're already running a CRM, ERP, WhatsApp or any business software, there's a good chance you're using a fraction of its potential — and losing hours to the gaps between systems. In a free 30-minute AI automation audit, we map your workflows and show you exactly where time and money are leaking, and what to automate first. You keep the plan either way. <a href=\"/#contact-form\">Book your free automation audit</a>.</p>\n",
